headline: 2 Fantastic Dividend Stocks to Buy in December
summary: Having cash regularly deposited in your account from dividend stocks is a great feeling.  It not only helps ease the sting of market volatility, but it can also help you build up a nice stream of income when you really need it in retirement.  Home Depot (NYSE: HD) has been a solid growth stock for many years.

headline: Stagflation Ahead?
summary: Fed upgraded inflation expectations, and reduced the number of projected cuts in 2025. This brings up the worst-case scenario fear for the market, stagflation.
